data.description: Discover elegance in this Meadowlane gem, nestled in a serene neighborhood near schools and shops. Boasting 1900 sq ft, this all-brick home features a mahogany Pella Craftsman door. Inside, stained maple cabinets, glass mosaic backsplash, and LED lighting adorn the kitchen. A stone fireplace graces the formal dining or family room. Step onto the 12x12 deck from sliding doors, with a nearby power source. Upstairs, 2 bedrooms offer ample closets, while the master opens to the deck. A 12X12 concrete slab awaits a hot tub, with a dedicated 20 amp outlet. The updated bathroom shines with solid surface countertops. The finished basement hosts a third bedroom, half bath, and bonus space for a closet or gym. This meticulously maintained home blends charm with modern comforts, offering timeless appeal in a coveted location. Don’t miss out—schedule a tour today!
